            <h1>Cabinet asks for briefing on Chamber proposals for economic sustainability</h1>
            <h2><p>&nbsp;BusinessToday has learnt that a&nbsp;report by a think tank set up by the Chamber of Commerce to propose scenarios for a sustainable and competitive economic future for Malta will be discussed by the Cabinet of Ministers when they meet on Tuesday</p></h2>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div></div>            </div>
